longBusinessSummary: SW Umwelttechnik Stoiser & Wolschner AG engages in the development and production of precast concrete elements for infrastructure construction in Austria, Hungary, Romania, and Slovakia. It offers mineral oil separators, wastewater treatment and purification products, sewage treatment plants, prestressed concrete tanks, wall systems, and drinking water storage systems. The company was founded in 1910 and is based in Klagenfurt, Austria.
